{"tid":1218411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好鬆懈，我地係輸緊！！保持心中既憤怒","createTime":"2019-06-13T15:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T08:40:51.000Z","uid":60662,"like":146,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8dcda57267039383f68e23255b50b52bffa5924b","tid":1218411,"uid":60662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"依家個環境好似風向轉咁，就係會令大家鬆懈。跟住政府拖拖下又會熄左大家團火。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>記住，呢一刻無贏任何野無爭取到任何野，係輸緊！！仲輸左幾百名義士。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家保持住團火，難得可以武勇、和理非、教徒團結一齊抗惡法，大家千其唔好篤灰，依家係大是大非既時候，呢兩日既情況已經展示左大家可以互相保護。<br />\n<br />\n我地依家目標應該係：<br />\n１.　撤回惡法，邊日開會就邊日野餐<br />\n２.　要黑警釋放所有因示威而被捕人士<br />\n３.　清算建制派，黑警，ＴＶＢ，偽人<br />\n４.　將琴日發生既圖／片不停轉發出去，等全世界都知<br />\n<br />\n果班被黑警圍嘔拘捕既義士，一定要救佢地，唔好留低佢地"},{"pid":"618d5d1203ae40e7498fbd1b16b3b0a46020dd55","tid":1218411,"uid":60662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:57:44.000Z","msg":"仲有見形勢改變就轉軚果班<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9700627e887107fad655873110ce53af411a9878","tid":1218411,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0688c63f99d65ccbc4a889b6cf0f7a37b058008c","tid":1218411,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:10:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"134068d28c309cdd7e8d1520646cc2d5cd2d9de8","tid":1218411,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8825041ea2fd39f8c3ab9539a04e5dcf58763d5a","tid":1218411,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac